MidPoint 4.10 "Braille" Update 2
--------------------------------

Release 4.10.2 is a seventy-sixth midPoint release code-named Braille.
The 4.10.2 release brings accessibility improvements and miscellaneous bugfixes.

Release date: 16th March 2026
Release type: Maintenance release
End of support: 25th November 2027

Please see the release notes for detailed list of changes:
https://docs.evolveum.com/midpoint/release/4.10.2/
